{"tid":1811470,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，今日小弟生日想各位幫我願望成真","createTime":"2020-01-04T17:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T14:59:44.000Z","uid":34355,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"955a4e357ca14e050b62317ca4cbf29d38e562ec","tid":1811470,"uid":34355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"先比張圖各位睇我真係今日生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e1NMbWZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe1NMbWZ.png&h=39fb4ed2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n每年既生日都係自己過，今年答正12點既時候許左個願，願望就係.....<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然哩D野唔係齋得個講字，所以我聽日會係北區搞個生日會，希望大家一齊黎同我慶祝，地點同時間已經係下面張圖上面，想見到我同一齊食放題就準時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6PPe5jQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6PPe5jQ.png&h=b15e55dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黎唔到既手足都唔緊要，希望你都可以影低張類似下面既圖黎為一月五生日既我送上祝福<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrBX25i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrBX25i.png&h=92d1b048&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n在此乞句生日快樂同有緣就聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb1e67e6132ad1860f7c0b6b41f4ae55ceb99b1","tid":1811470,"uid":22564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T17:15:58.000Z","msg":"生日快樂"},{"pid":"1c8c5647a95e141db4e60